Are these detections of CP in the archival SMA data shown real or are they
 instrumental artifacts? This is our chief concern because of the difficulty
 of calibrating CP measurements and because the measurements presented here
 were not made with any special considerations for calibrating CP as in
 the observation of Sgr A* reported in 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
